OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome sunshine and a frost first
OL,6,Fthing in the morning for many. The
OL,7,Frest of the day will then be dry,
OL,8,Fbright with best of sun along east
OL,9,Fcoast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FPartly cloudy this evening
OL,12,Fwith some late hazy sunshine. The rest
OL,13,Fof the night will be predominately dry
OL,14,Fwith clear spells, but a few showers
OL,15,Fpossible across Upper Tayside.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FA bright morning with hazy
OL,18,Fsunny spells. Cloud will tend to
OL,19,Fdevelop through the day and bring a
OL,20,Ffew showers, some of which may be on
OL,21,Fthe heavy side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
